{"type": "article", "id": 9885, "title": "Stellar Works 系列家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-22T07:26:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135623IvVOEyDGtSQgsa8L.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是 Yabu Pushelberg 为 Stellar Works 推出的系列家具，包括椅子，咖啡桌，边桌、双人沙发、屏风以及不同型号的陈列柜。整个系列采用浅珊瑚和浅灰配色，每件作品都有着憨厚的形态和温柔的线条，营造出甜蜜而轻快的气氛。目前作品正在伦敦克勒肯维尔设计周上进行展出。<a href=\"http://www.clerkenwelldesignweek.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看设计周详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135621EJtG12oFqDLna4pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061356228wDiY5RyE240UMcH.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60880196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135622dK9QLmY5NfGDr7SV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59779951\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135623JrH0Y1yWeSGz3miF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}